  "text": "In order to determine the similarity of the traffic on the communication links, we make use of traffic-flow pattern matching [CITATION_1] . There are two separate procedures in pattern matching: trend-pattern matching and volume-pattern matching. Traffic pattern matching is done in sentinels and the results are collected by the protection agent, which will construct the attack paths.",
